Detailed Description

PrefExtLangProvider is the provider to retrieve and manipulate the EF-ELP file of the sim (GSM 11.11 V8.2.0 10.1.2). An instance of this class is part of the Apoxi Data Control. A pointer to this provider can be retrieved from the main provider via the id:

c_preflang_provider_id

In case of UMTS build a second instance is used which can be retrieved with

c_preflang2_provider_id

In case of UMTS build and USIM c_preflang_provider_id will retrieve the file EF-LI and c_preflang2_provider_id will retrieve EF-PL. In case of EDGE/GPRS and SIM only c_preflang_provider_id shall be used as it represents EF-ELP.

Following column ids are defined: c_ext_lang_pref_id :WStringType

NOTE: Please do not instantiate this class.
